<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<%- include('partials/head') %>

<body>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

  <section class="hero-section text-center">
    <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold text-warning mb-4">Welcome to What's in the Box?</h1>
    <p class="lead fs-5 text-light mb-4 px-3">
      Hey there! We’re two young devs on a mission to bring a little mystery and fun to your day — one box at a time.
    </p>
    <p class="lead fs-5 text-light mb-4 px-3">
      Each day brings a new mystery box — a single image, quietly waiting to be discovered. Some may make you smile, others may make you pause. Each one is a small reminder: even the unexpected has value, if we take a moment to look.
    </p>
    
    <p class="lead fs-5 text-light mb-4 px-3">
      Some boxes are common. Some are legendary. Some might make you laugh — or question reality. Collect, trade, or just enjoy the chaos. It's your daily dose of "what the heck?"
    </p>
    <button class="btn btn-box mt-3" onclick="window.location.href='/open'">Open Today’s Box</button>
  </section>

  <!-- Cards Section -->
  <section class="container my-5">
    <div class="row text-center">
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow rounded-4 bg-dark text-light">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-warning">🎯 Rarity-Based Loot</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Open boxes with items ranging from common trinkets to ultra-rare collectibles. What you get depends on luck!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow rounded-4 bg-dark text-light">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-warning">🎨 Cool & Quirky Art</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Discover original images, mini artworks, memes, and visual surprises that make each box worth opening.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow rounded-4 bg-dark text-light">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title text-warning">🤝 Trade & Flex</h5>
            <p class="card-text">
              Join our community to trade items, show off your rarest finds, and see what others have uncovered!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
